OL,3,CShould authorities have told us more
OL,4,Cabout the Southport killer?
OL,6,FViolent disorder was seen across the
OL,7,FUK after Axel Rudakubana killed three
OL,8,Fgirls and attempted to kill ten others
OL,9,Fat a Taylor Swift-themed dance class
OL,10,Fin Southport on July 29 last year.
OL,12,FIn the hours after the attack
OL,13,Fincorrect details about the attacker,
OL,14,Fincluding that he was an asylum
OL,15,Fseeker, circulated online, sparking
OL,16,Friots that were fuelled by
OL,17,Fdisinformation that grew in an
OL,18,Finformation vacuum.
