OL,3,CShould authorities have told us more
OL,4,Cabout the Southport killer?
OL,6,FIn a Downing Street press conference
OL,7,Fearlier this week, the Prime Minister
OL,8,Fdefended the decision taken by
OL,9,Fauthorities not to share information
OL,10,Fabout the case earlier, saying that to
OL,11,Fdo so would have risked collapsing a
OL,12,Fpotential jury trial. He also
OL,13,Fannounced there would be a review of
OL,14,Fcontempt of court legislation in the
OL,15,Fwake of the riots.
OL,17,FBut as rioters began feeding off their
OL,18,Ffalse theories in other towns and
OL,19,Fcities in summer 2024 - ITV News looks
OL,20,Fat whether authorities should have
OL,21,Ftold us more.
