OL,6,FWhat are the current contempt of court
OL,7,Flaw?
OL,9,FUnder the Contempt of Court Act 1981
OL,10,Fyou are not allowed to say or write
OL,11,Fanything publicly that could prejudice
OL,12,Fa trial.
OL,14,FContempt of court laws exist to
OL,15,Fprevent interference in legal
OL,16,Fproceedings and apply to everyone,
OL,17,Ffrom journalists to online
OL,18,Fcommentators publishing information on
OL,19,Fsocial media.
