OL,3,CShould authorities have told us more
OL,4,Cabout the Southport killer?
OL,6,FFor example, ITV News was able to
OL,7,Fbroadcast CCTV of Axel Rudakubana
OL,8,Fafter he was arrested but before he
OL,9,Fhad been charged and to debunk the
OL,10,Fmyth that he was an asylum seeker or a
OL,11,FMuslim.
OL,13,FWhy are they needed?
OL,15,FIn 2010, former teacher Christopher
OL,16,FJefferies had been arrested on
OL,17,Fsuspicion of murdering his tenant
OL,18,FJoanna Yeates in Bristol.
