OL,3,CShould authorities have told us more
OL,4,Cabout the Southport killer?
OL,6,FHe was released and later another man,
OL,7,FVincent Tabak, was jailed for her
OL,8,Fmurder. But in the intervening months
OL,9,FMr Jefferies suffered character
OL,10,Fassassination by many tabloids.
OL,12,FIt is cases like this that experts say
OL,13,Fthe law should not be changed.
