OL,3,CShould authorities have told us more
OL,4,Cabout the Southport killer?
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, Former Justice
OL,7,FSecretary, Sir Robert Buckland said
OL,8,Fthat the criticism aimed at
OL,9,Fauthorities for not releasing
OL,10,Finformation was "blaming those who are
OL,11,Fprotecting the rule of law for
OL,12,Funlawful and criminal rioting and
OL,13,Fpublic disorder that we saw on our
OL,14,Fstreets".
OL,16,FHe added: "We all know who is to blame
OL,17,Ffor that, it's the people who did it
OL,18,Fthemselves, the perpetrators. I think
OL,19,Fwe should think long and hard before
OL,20,Fupending a system that is there to
OL,21,Fserve the interests of justice."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
