OL,3,CShould authorities have told us more
OL,4,Cabout the Southport killer?
OL,6,FMr Hall told ITV's Good Morning
OL,7,FBritain: "It really is hard to see why
OL,8,Fmore information couldn't have been
OL,9,Fgiven to the public ` they were crying
OL,10,Fout.
OL,12,F"How the CPS, how the police, how the
OL,13,Fauthorities approach giving
OL,14,Finformation when these terrible
OL,15,Fattacks occur has to be thought about
OL,16,Fin the social media age.
OL,18,F"Just saying nothing is no longer an
OL,19,Foption."
