OL,3,CShould authorities have told us more
OL,4,Cabout the Southport killer?
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said:
OL,7,F"It is true that we live in a
OL,8,Fdifferent age, in that available
OL,9,Finformation is now available online as
OL,10,Fwell as offline, and I understand the
OL,11,Ffrustration of all, including some
OL,12,Fjournalists, who observe the rules and
OL,13,Fdon't report what they know because
OL,14,Fthey know that the law doesn't permit
OL,15,Fit, and it runs the risk of collapsing
OL,16,Fa trial, only to see information
OL,17,Fonline that doesn't appear to be
OL,18,Ffollowing the same rules, and that is
OL,19,Fnot acceptable."
